about Dad,

14:08.456 --> 14:10.806
maybe you should see what
he said about you first.

14:10.850 --> 14:12.416
What do you mean?

14:12.460 --> 14:15.332
This is Dad's goodbye letter
to you.

14:15.376 --> 14:17.813
I wasn't gonna deliver it
because I wanted to protect you.

14:17.857 --> 14:20.511
Mine was horrible,
and I was his favorite.

14:20.555 --> 14:23.079
But if you still want to "honor"
him after you've read this,

14:23.123 --> 14:25.516
knock yourself out.

14:25.560 --> 14:27.823
"Dear Fuck Face.

14:27.867 --> 14:30.782
