a child, until I met you."

14:30.826 --> 14:32.915
It gets worse from there.

14:32.959 --> 14:35.918
Oh!

14:35.962 --> 14:37.137
Oh!

14:38.878 --> 14:45.493
We will all miss
Jim Brockmire, Sr. --

14:45.536 --> 14:49.714
husband, father, employee,

14:49.758 --> 14:53.109
a man observed
by all around him.

14:53.153 --> 14:56.112
Born many years ago...

14:56.156 --> 14:59.072
