the sun of his cruelty

15:17.351 --> 15:19.831
till it is burned into
my frontal lobe, okay?

15:19.875 --> 15:21.572
I will never, ever again

15:21.616 --> 15:24.053
let time soften my memory
of that man.

15:24.097 --> 15:25.620
Jim...

15:25.663 --> 15:28.231
Can you believe I wanted
to give him a nice eulogy?

15:28.275 --> 15:32.583
