on the negative,

16:03.614 --> 16:06.791
go up there,
shit all over your father,

16:06.835 --> 16:09.316
and accomplish
absolutely nothing

16:09.359 --> 16:12.667
except making everything more
painful than it already is.

16:14.364 --> 16:16.845
You're absolutely right.

16:16.888 --> 16:19.108
Jim most assuredly --

16:19.152 --> 16:21.328
Guess I should've given him
a third option.

16:21.371 --> 16:26.463
