You can hit the showers.

16:32.643 --> 16:33.905
You're relieved, seriously.

16:33.949 --> 16:36.560
Thank you.

16:36.604 --> 16:38.475
I'm sorry, but, um,

16:38.519 --> 16:40.303
if we're gonna say goodbye
to Dad here today,

16:40.347 --> 16:42.566
