you were spooning out there.

16:55.188 --> 16:57.799
I have no positive memories
of my father.

16:57.842 --> 16:59.975
Seriously, not one.

17:00.019 --> 17:02.717
He wasn't so much a dad
as he was just this --

17:02.760 --> 17:05.807
this angry creep
who would stalk around the house

17:05.849 --> 17:07.416
on evenings and weekends.

17:07.461 --> 17:09.637
So he tried to find some peace
every day

17:09.680 --> 17:12.074
during what he called
"Tiki Time."

17:12.117 --> 17:16.339
Tiki Time was when he'd go out
to this old bamboo bar

17:16.383 --> 17:18.298
that he had constructed
out in the garage,

17:18.340 --> 17:20.387
and he would throw back Mai Tais
out there.

17:20.430 --> 17:22.388
Now, we never were allowed
to disturb him then

17:22.432 --> 17:26.915
because, as Dad liked to put it,
Tiki Time was paradise.

17:26.958 --> 17:30.310
But one night,
I desecrated Tiki Time

17:30.353 --> 17:32.355
when I went out there to
tell him that he had forgotten

17:32.399 --> 17:34.401
to feed us kids dinner
that night.

17:34.444 --> 17:36.838
So, he stormed back
into the house,

17:36.881 --> 17:38.448
and he nuked up some fish sticks

17:38.492 --> 17:40.102
till they were just
hotter than the sun,

17:40.146 --> 17:42.104
and then screamed into our faces

17:42.148 --> 17:44.715
when we wanted to wait
for them to cool down.

17:51.374 --> 17:52.984
I don't remember anything
after that

17:53.028 --> 17:55.465
except for, well, waking up
in the emergency room,

17:55.509 --> 17:58.729
where Jean and I
had, uh, third-degree burns.

18:00.122 --> 18:03.952
I guess things might've been
easier if Mom had stuck around,

18:03.995 --> 18:05.867
but, you know,
I never blamed her leaving.

18:05.910 --> 18:08.130
Hell, I ran away
the first chance that I got,

18:08.174 --> 18:11.655
uh, which left my sister, Jean,
at home holding the bag.

18:11.699 --> 18:16.007
And by "bag," of course,
I am referring to shithead
down there.

18:16.051 --> 18:18.227
Somehow though, Jean,

18:18.271 --> 18:20.534
y-you came out of that
in better shape than I did.

18:20.577 --> 18:22.275
I don't know how you did that.

18:22.318 --> 18:24.146
I guess it's 'cause
you were wise enough

18:24.190 --> 18:26.714
