with a family of your own.

18:26.757 --> 18:29.151
I mean, don't get me wrong.

18:29.195 --> 18:32.154
I wouldn't trade places with you
if you put a shotgun
in my mouth,

18:32.198 --> 18:36.071
but, uh, no, I still envy you
all the same.

18:36.115 --> 18:39.030
And you were right.
You were right.
I have not changed.

18:39.074 --> 18:41.816
I managed to make this moment
all about myself, didn't I?

18:41.859 --> 18:45.124
But what can I say?
I'm not over my past, obviously,

18:45.167 --> 18:47.604
and still quite trapped by it.

18:47.648 --> 18:50.259
But, you know, very difficult
for scars to heal

18:50.303 --> 18:52.783
when the knife's still stickin'
out of the wound there, huh?

18:54.742 --> 18:56.613
That past isn't really the past,
anyway, is it?

18:56.657 --> 18:59.007
I mean, is it?
Nobody changes.

18:59.050 --> 19:02.445
Nobody actually matures.
I mean, uh, he didn't.

19:02.489 --> 19:06.188
He remained a monster
till the day he died.

19:06.232 --> 19:08.190
And now he even looks like one.

19:10.192 --> 19:13.369
Anywhoodles, Dad's gone.

19:13.413 --> 19:17.591
