That --

19:47.882 --> 19:50.624
Boy, it's so weird where
we're in a place where
that actually --

19:50.667 --> 19:53.888
That just gave me
some comfort.

19:53.931 --> 19:57.718
I still feel, uh,
pretty awful, though.

19:57.761 --> 20:01.243
Would you feel better
if we had sex?

20:01.287 --> 20:05.247
