characteristic.

20:08.555 --> 20:10.426
As much as I'd love
to show you everything

20:10.470 --> 20:12.515
that I learned in
the knock shops of Manila,

20:12.559 --> 20:14.474
my dad's letter is still kind of
stripping the paint

20:14.517 --> 20:15.866
right off of my insides.

20:15.910 --> 20:17.825
So, I-I'm just not sure
I could handle

20:17.868 --> 20:21.959
